songs.title: Fly High (Interlude)
songs.lyrics:
Baby
You make me, want to, be with you
Baby
Come with two and I'll take you on a ride
Let's f-l-y-y-y-y
Ohhhhhhh
H-i-i-i-i-g-g-g-h-h
Space age life
Niggas tryna do it like me
But they can't do it right, yeah
Waited my whole life
For this very moment, I promised to God that I won't lose sight, yeah
